class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>\n\t\t<span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n\t\t\tresolve<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token string\">`gatsby-plugin-paddle`</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n\t\t\toptions<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n\t\t\t\tvendorId<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'YOUR_VENDOR_ID'</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// Find in your account settings.</span>\n\t\t\t\tdebug<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token boolean\">false</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// Set true to start the debug mode.</span>\n\t\t\t<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\t\t<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\t<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>","timeToRead":1}}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/packages/gatsby-plugin-paddle/","id":"c0743cfe-2ab1-53be-8723-26d30a365aa3","layout":"plugins"}}